reviewText: Era of swing, a great time and the revivals groups about today. Banck on to subject matter, Beautiful music, nice jazz.  Now Jack Teagarden, a great jazz maestro, love Stars Fell On Alabama,  Rockin' Chair, (Old Aunt Harriet ah Well) Nobody Knows the Trouble I've Seen and many others, love his style- plays a great trombone..  He's a cool cat from Texas. Fantastic.  Just Love it.  Kindest Regards  Alfred P Barr
